com.facebook.buck.event.listener

Class TimeCostEntry<T extends BuckEvent>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.event.listener.TimeCostEntry<T>

  • public class TimeCostEntry<T extends BuckEvent>
extends Object
    Data class for storing the amortized time and total time of a start/finished event pair.

    // MOE:begin_strip

    Amortized time is considered to be this event's share of the total time spent. See AmortizedShareComputation for an explanation of how amortized time is computed. // MOE:end_strip
